        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Note that exactly what `locals()` does inside function scopes is currently not well defined by the language spec. [PEP 558](https://peps.python.org/pep-0558/) is currently being proposed to standardise a specific behaviour, which is actually to return a fresh dict each time like Cython does.",
